{
  "stem": "734.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then I saw several trucks of Polish prisoners of war, bandaged, torn uniforms, no hats, not shaven, raggedy, standing on the, on those trucks like cattle for slaughter.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And this gave me a very, ah, sad sort of commentary.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I thought, how could they ever withstand this type of an army-- ridiculous, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ba-- some of them had heads bandaged, the prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of them had the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] arms in these slings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Terrible-- what a picture that was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And eventually, I got-- I, I started feeling kind of very-- how shall I say-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] kind of like drunk, practically.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I realized that the exhaust from all these vehicles, the diesel exhaust, must've had an effect on me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The air was getting dark from all this exhaust, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I ran back to the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was almost like I was getting a headache.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother was alarmed over the fact that I wasn't there for hours.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She didn't know what happened to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, I told her where I was and what I saw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember, my-- we were all-- everybody was home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I told them what I saw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and I said to my father, I just can't understand how anyone in the world can withstand such an army.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my father said to me, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The English and the French, they'll take care of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Optimism-- they were very optimistic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was optimistic up to a point.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But at that time, of course, it was too early really to tell what was in store for us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he could afford to be an optimist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "For some reason, I wasn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I read He hadn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
